& C. Holtz-Bacha (Eds.). Journalism education in Europe and north America: An
international comparison. New Jersey: Hampton Press of Cresskill.

Williams, S. L. (1929). Twenty years of education for journalism. Columbia:
E.W. Stephens Publishing Co.

